<div class="any-panel-wide">
  <div class="mb-4">
    <div class="relative bg-blue-100 border-l-4 border-blue-500 text-blue-700 p-4" role="alert">
      <svg class="cursor-pointer absolute top-0 pt-2 right-0 pr-2 fill-current w-8 h-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path class="heroicon-ui" d="M5 3h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5c0-1.1.9-2 2-2zm0 2v14h14V5H5zm8.41 7l1.42 1.41a1 1 0 1 1-1.42 1.42L12 13.4l-1.41 1.42a1 1 0 1 1-1.42-1.42L10.6 12l-1.42-1.41a1 1 0 1 1 1.42-1.42L12 10.6l1.41-1.42a1 1 0 1 1 1.42 1.42L13.4 12z"/></svg>
      <p class="font-bold">Welcome to AnyCable demo appâ€”AnyWork!</p>
      <p>AnyWork allows you to create <em>workspaces</em> containing one or many TODO lists and, of course,
      a chat (because no real-time framework demo could exist without chats ðŸ˜‰).</p>
      <p>All changes within a workspace are propagated to all the open pages (aka connected clients), so everyone stays in sync.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h2 class="mb-2">Open existing workspace</h2>
    <form class="flex items-center border-b border-b-2 border-red mb-4 pb-1">
      <input class="any-text-input" type="text" placeholder="Workspace ID">
      <button class="flex-shrink-0 any-button" type="submit">
        Open
      </button>
    </form>
    <div class="flex items-center">
      <div>...or </div>
      <%= link_to "Create", new_workspace_path, class: "any-button-outlined ml-2 mr-2 no-underline" %>
      <div> a new one!</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <% if @recent_workspaces.any? %>
    <div class="mt-10">
      <h2 class="mb-2">Recently viewed workspaces</h2>
      <ul>
        <% @recent_workspaces.each do |workspace| %>
          <li><%= link_to workspace.name, workspace %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
